<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Obviously it wasn=E2=80=99t=C2=A0<em>just=C2=
=A0</em>a joke. When Lowe went to a conference and said that MoviePass trac=
ked customers=C2=A0through their phones and collected and monetized lots of=
