<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Three possible models for Elon Musk=E2=80=99s =
acquisition of Twitter Inc. are:</p>
<ol style=3D"list-style-type: decimal; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;"=
>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Musk is a business genius, and will f=
ind a way to make Twitter much more valuable. This seems to be <a href=3D"h=
ttps://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/29619421.264507/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3=
cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjItMTAtMDMvZXZlcnlvbmUtd2Fud=
GVkLXRvLWJ1eS10d2l0dGVyLXdpdGgtZWxvbj9jbXBpZD1CQkQxMTA3MjJfTU9ORVlTVFVGRiZ1=
dG1fbWVkaXVtPWVtYWlsJnV0bV9zb3VyY2U9bmV3c2xldHRlciZ1dG1fdGVybT0yMjExMDcmdXR=
tX2NhbXBhaWduPW1vbmV5c3R1ZmY/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB3ccc1bb5" itemprop=3D=
"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #0000=
00; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bott=
om-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">  t=
he theory</a> of Musk=E2=80=99s equity co-investors, for instance.</li>=09<=
li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Musk doesn=E2=80=99t care about making mon=
ey, but he=C2=A0has a philosophical commitment to promoting free speech and=
 vigorous debate on Twitter, the modern town square. This seems to be <a hr=
ef=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/29619421.264507/aHR0cHM=
6Ly93d3cudGhldmVyZ2UuY29tLzIwMjIvNC8xNC8yMzAyNTM0My9lbG9uLW11c2stdHdpdHRlci=
10YWtlb3Zlci10ZWQtdGFsay1xdW90ZS1zdG9jay1idXlvdXQ/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB=
ee9a9c38" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" =
style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-wi=
dth: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; backgro=
und-color: #ccc;"> Musk=E2=80=99s theory</a>, sometimes.</li>=09<li style=
=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Musk is very=C2=A0rich and very addicted to Twitte=
r, and buying Twitter lets him be the boss of Twitter and make his own expe=
rience more fun, or possibly=C2=A0<em>less</em> fun but in a way that feeds=
 his addiction. This was more or less <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloomber=
gbusiness.com/click/29619421.264507/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGl=
uaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjItMDQtMDQvZWxvbi1tdXNrLWJvdWdodC1zb21lLXR3aXR0ZXI_Y2=
1waWQ9QkJEMTEwNzIyX01PTkVZU1RVRkYmdXRtX21lZGl1bT1lbWFpbCZ1dG1fc291cmNlPW5ld=
3NsZXR0ZXImdXRtX3Rlcm09MjIxMTA3JnV0bV9jYW1wYWlnbj1tb25leXN0dWZm/607f07ceef4=
b8524a319a23cBb325a913" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" targ=
et=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; bo=
rder-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: =
solid; background-color: #ccc;">  my original theory of the deal</a>.</li>
</ol>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">In Musk=E2=80=99s unfathomably long <a href=3D=
